plt.figure(figsize=(6,6), dpi=600)
sns.set(font='sans serif')
sns.set(style="whitegrid")

ax=sns.barplot(x=inos['Condition '], y=inos['Positive cells']/inos['Cells']*100, data=inos, color="#c51b8a",ci=None)

sample_sizes = [1093, 438, 429, 704, 784, 620, 475, 501, 710] 

for p, n in zip(ax.patches, sample_sizes):
    ax.text(
        p.get_x() + p.get_width() / 2.,  # X position: center of the bar
        p.get_height() + 1,              # Y position: slightly above the bar
        f'n={n}',                        # Text format, adjust if needed
        ha='center', va='bottom',        # Center align horizontally and slightly above
        fontsize=10                      # Font size for the text
    )

ax.set(xticklabels=["mock", "LPS", "recovery", "10", "15", "30", "50", "100", "200"])  
ax.tick_params(axis='x', labelsize=12)
ax.tick_params(axis='y', labelsize=12)
ax.set(xlabel=None)
ax.set_ylabel("iNOS+ cells (%)", fontsize=15)          
plt.ylim(0,50)

In [10]:
plt.figure(figsize=(5,5), dpi=600)
sns.set(font='sans serif')
sns.set(style="whitegrid")

ax=sns.barplot(x=ns4b['Condition'], y=ns4b['NS4B+ cells']/ns4b['Cells']*100, data=ns4b, hue=ns4b['Infection'], palette=["#e7e6e0","#e5c81d"],ci=None)

comparisons = [("mock", "LPS_24h"), ("LPS_24h", "LPS_30d"), ("mock","LPS_30d")]

annotator = Annotator(ax, comparisons, data=ns4b, x="Condition", y=ns4b['NS4B+ cells']/ns4b['Cells']*100)
annotator.configure(test='t-test_ind', text_format='star', loc='inside', verbose=2)
annotator.apply_and_annotate()

ax.legend(title="Infection status")
ax.set(xticklabels=["mock", "24h-LPS", "30d-LPS"])  
ax.tick_params(axis='x', labelsize=15)
ax.tick_params(axis='y', labelsize=15)
ax.set(xlabel=None)
ax.set_ylabel("NS4B+ cells (%)", fontsize=18)          
plt.ylim(0,20)

plt.figure(figsize=(4,4), dpi=600)
sns.set(font='sans serif')
sns.set(style="whitegrid")

ax=sns.barplot(x=inos['Time point'], y=inos['Positive cells (%)'], data=inos, color="#c51b8a", label='iNOS+ cells (%)')

sample_sizes = [1647, 1276, 1193, 757] 

for p, n in zip(ax.patches, sample_sizes):
    ax.text(
        p.get_x() + p.get_width() / 2.,  # X position: center of the bar
        p.get_height() + 1,              # Y position: slightly above the bar
        f'n={n}',                        # Text format, adjust if needed
        ha='center', va='bottom',        # Center align horizontally and slightly above
        fontsize=10                      # Font size for the text
    )

    
comparisons = [("6h", "24h"), ("24h", "48h"), ("mock","48h")]

annotator = Annotator(ax, comparisons, data=inos, x="Time point", y="Positive cells (%)")
annotator.configure(test='t-test_ind', text_format='star', loc='inside', verbose=2)
annotator.apply_and_annotate()

ax.tick_params(axis='x', labelsize=15)
ax.tick_params(axis='y', labelsize=15)
ax.set_xlabel('Incubation time', fontsize=16)
ax.set_ylabel('iNOS+ cells (%)', fontsize=16)
plt.ylim(0,100)
